# Normalize line endings to LF everywhere. Node's writeFileSync
# produces LF; git's core.autocrlf=true (Windows default) converts to
# CRLF on checkout. Without this, generated-file drift checks
# (docs/TOOLS.md, README.md) false-trigger on CRLF/LF mismatch.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Installer shell scripts need CRLF for Windows cmd.exe.
# build-installer.ts handles this via copyAsCrlf at staging time,
# so source stays LF; only the staged/shipped copies get CRLF.
